statements.sql: select "c"."id", "idnumber", "summary", "summaryformat", "startdate", "enddate", "shortname", "fullname", "category", "visible", "ctx"."id" as "ctxid", "ctx"."path" as "ctxpath", "ctx"."depth" as "ctxdepth", "ctx"."contextlevel" as "ctxlevel", "ctx"."instanceid" as "ctxinstance", "ctx"."locked" as "ctxlocked" from "mdl_course" as "c" inner join "mdl_context" as "ctx" on "ctx"."instanceid" = "c"."id" and "ctx"."contextlevel" = '50' inner join "mdl_user_lastaccess" as "ul" on "ul"."courseid" = "c"."id" left join "mdl_favourite" as "fav" on "fav"."itemid" = "ul"."courseid" and "fav"."component" = 'core_course' and "fav"."itemtype" = 'courses' and "fav"."userid" = 7 left join "mdl_enrol" as "eg" on "eg"."courseid" = "c"."id" and "eg"."status" = '0' and "eg"."enrol" = 'guest' where "ul"."userid" = 7 and "c"."visible" = 1 and ("eg"."id" is not null or exists (select "e"."id" from "mdl_enrol" as "e" inner join "mdl_user_enrolments" as "ue" on "ue"."enrolid" = "e"."id" where "e"."courseid" = "c"."id" and "e"."status" = '0' and "ue"."status" = '0' and "ue"."userid" = 3 and "ue"."timestart" < 1739895283 and ("ue"."timeend" = 0 or "ue"."timeend" > 1739895283))) order by "timeaccess" desc limit 2

select "c"."id" as "courseid", "c"."fullname", COUNT(DISTINCT cmc.id) as completed_activities, COUNT(DISTINCT cm.id) as total_activities, ROUND((COUNT(DISTINCT cmc.id) * 100.0) / COUNT(DISTINCT cm.id), 2) as completion_percentage from "mdl_course" as "c" inner join "mdl_course_modules" as "cm" on "cm"."course" = "c"."id" left join "mdl_course_modules_completion" as "cmc" on "cmc"."coursemoduleid" = "cm"."id" and "cmc"."userid" = 3 and "cmc"."completionstate" = 1 where "cm"."completion" > 0 and 0 = 1 group by "c"."id", "c"."fullname"

select "c"."id", "c"."category", "c"."sortorder", "c"."shortname", "c"."fullname", "c"."idnumber", "c"."startdate", "c"."visible", "c"."groupmode", "c"."groupmodeforce", "c"."cacherev", "c"."summary", "c"."summaryformat", "c"."enddate", "ctx"."id" as "ctxid", "ctx"."path" as "ctxpath", "ctx"."depth" as "ctxdepth", "ctx"."contextlevel" as "ctxlevel", "ctx"."instanceid" as "ctxinstance", "ctx"."locked" as "ctxlocked" from "mdl_course" as "c" inner join (select distinct "e"."courseid" from "mdl_enrol" as "e" inner join "mdl_user_enrolments" as "ue" on "ue"."enrolid" = "e"."id" and "ue"."userid" = 3 and "ue"."status" = 0 and "e"."status" = 0 and "ue"."timestart" <= 1739895283 and ("ue"."timeend" = 0 or "ue"."timeend" > 1739895283)) as "en" on "en"."courseid" = "c"."id" left join "mdl_context" as "ctx" on "ctx"."instanceid" = "c"."id" and "ctx"."contextlevel" = 50 where "c"."id" <> 1 order by "c"."visible" desc, "c"."fullname" asc

select "e".*, "c"."fullname" as "coursefullname", "c"."shortname" as "courseshortname", "cs"."name" as "sectionname", "cs"."section" as "sectionnumber" from "mdl_event" as "e" left join "mdl_modules" as "m" on "e"."modulename" = "m"."name" left join "mdl_course" as "c" on "c"."id" = "e"."courseid" left join "mdl_course_modules" as "cm" on "cm"."instance" = "e"."instance" and "cm"."module" = CAST(m.id as BIGINT) and "cm"."course" = CAST(c.id as BIGINT) left join "mdl_course_sections" as "cs" on "cs"."id" = "cm"."section" where "e"."visible" = 1 and (("e"."userid" = 3 and "e"."courseid" = 0 and "e"."groupid" = 0 and "e"."categoryid" = 0) or ("e"."groupid" = 0 and "e"."courseid" in (3, 1) and "e"."categoryid" = 0) or ("e"."groupid" = 0 and "e"."courseid" = 0 and "e"."categoryid" = 2)) and ("e"."timestart" >= 1739895283 or e.timestart + e.timeduration > 1739895283) and ("m"."visible" = 1 or "m"."visible" is null) order by COALESCE(e.timesort, e.timestart) asc, "e"."id" asc limit 10
